sdl:
schema  { query: query_root }

type article_aggregate { avg: article_aggregate_avg
  count: article_aggregate_count
  nodes: [article_fields!]!
  sum: article_aggregate_sum
}

type article_aggregate_avg { authorId: Int
  id: Int
}

type article_aggregate_count { authorId: Int!
  content: Int!
  id: Int!
  title: Int!
}

type article_aggregate_sum { authorId: Int
  id: Int
}

type article_fields { authorId: Int
  content: String
  id: Int
  title: String
}

type article_group { group_aggregate: article_aggregate!
  group_key: article_fields!
}

type author_aggregate { avg: author_aggregate_avg
  count: author_aggregate_count
  nodes: [author_fields!]!
  sum: author_aggregate_sum
}

type author_aggregate_avg { id: Int
}

type author_aggregate_count { id: Int!
  name: Int!
}

type author_aggregate_sum { id: Int
}

type author_fields { id: Int
  name: String
}

type author_group { group_aggregate: author_aggregate!
  group_key: author_fields!
}

type query_root { article_aggregate(where: article_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): article_aggregate!
  article_find_one_by_id: article_fields
  article_group(group_by: [article_field!], where: article_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): [article_group!]!
  article_list(where: article_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): [article_fields!]!
  author_aggregate(where: author_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): author_aggregate!
  author_find_one_by_id: author_fields
  author_group(group_by: [author_field!], where: author_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): [author_group!]!
  author_list(where: author_boolean_expression, limit: Int, limit: Int): [author_fields!]!
}

enum article_field {authorId 
  content 
  id 
  title 
}

enum author_field {id 
  name 
}

input Int_comparison_expression {_eq: Int
}

input String_comparison_expression {_eq: String
}

input article_boolean_expression {_and: [article_boolean_expression!]
  _not: article_boolean_expression
  _or: [article_boolean_expression!]
  authorId: Int_comparison_expression
  content: String_comparison_expression
  id: Int_comparison_expression
  title: String_comparison_expression
}

input author_boolean_expression {_and: [author_boolean_expression!]
  _not: author_boolean_expression
  _or: [author_boolean_expression!]
  id: Int_comparison_expression
  name: String_comparison_expression
}
